# C# coding standards

Follow `docs/coding-standards/csharp-coding-standards.md` and root `.editorconfig`.

## Quick rules

- File-scoped namespaces; one public type per file
- `_camelCase` private fields; `PascalCase` types; `Async` suffix on async methods
- Always braces; `var` when type is apparent
- Sort usings: System* first; remove unused
- `sealed` unless designed for inheritance
- Platform 2.0: no ABP in new modules; use `Add<Context>Module` / `Map<Context>Endpoints`

Akka-specific rules: `AkkaSignalRVuePoc/.cursor/rules/csharp-resharper-style.mdc`.
